[SDG-GLYPHS]: Switch between TYPE/EXEC/TERM modes by drawing the exec or term glyph as your first stroke
[SDG-GLYPHS]: Record custom glyphs in record mode by drawing the same shape in each grid cell
[SDG-GLYPHS]: Use dictionary mode to browse all built-in glyphs with animated stroke previews
[SDG-GLYPHS]: Strike through a recognised glyph label to remove it from the session
[SDG-GLYPHS]: The carousel bar at the bottom shows all available glyphs with live animations
[SDG-GLYPHS]: Draw a circle to execute the current session
